    <title>Customer Management</title>
    <conbody>
        <section>
            <p><ph conref="../../Shared/Product_Name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"
                /> offers various features for managing your organization's interaction with customers. Customer management involves the following tasks:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Registering customers.</li>
                <li>Configuring an external user authentication system, if required.</li>
                <li>Handling subscriptions.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>These tasks are described in more detail in the sections below.</p>
        </section>
    </conbody>
